| Obey script for Colloquy talker server under RISC OS

| Set file path origin and dynamic heap
|RMEnsure DDEUtils 0.00 RMLoad System:Module.DDEUtils
|Prefix <Obey$Dir>.dist-riscos-arm
Set Colloquy$Heap ""
Set Colloquy$Dir <Obey$Dir>.dist-riscos-arm

| Launch resolver component of the talker server
WimpTask TaskWindow "<Colloquy$Dir>.colloquy -f <Colloquy$Dir>/resolver.lua >null: 2>null:" -wimpslot 700K -name ColloquyResolver

| Launch talker server
WimpTask TaskWindow "<Colloquy$Dir>.colloquy" -wimpslot 700K -name ColloquyTalker